
<input type="hidden" name="target" value="HPI">
<input type="hidden" name="type" value="problem">
<input type="hidden" name="supportType" value="problem">


<h4 class="icon-card__title">Bereich auswählen</h4>
<span class="icon-card__subtitle">Welchen Bereich der Schul-Cloud betrifft dein Thema?</span>
<center>
<label class="form-group col-md-6">
		<span class="control-label"><i class="info_text fa fa-info-circle"></i> Bitte sende jedes Thema einzeln ab.</span>
		<select class="form-control" name="problemArea" id="problemArea" aria-placeholder="Bereich wählen">
			<option value="" disabled selected hidden>Bereich wählen</option>
			<option value="1">Übersicht</option>
			<optgroup label="Kurse"> 
				<option value="2">Themen</option>
				<optgroup label="Tools">
					<option value="3">BBB Videokonferenz</option>
					<option value="4">Bettermarks</option>
				</optgroup>
				<option value="5">Texteditor</option>
			</optgroup>
			<optgroup label="Teams">
				<option value="6">Libre Office</option>
				<option value="7">Neuigkeiten</option>
				<option value="8">Termine</option>
				<option value="9">Messenger</option>
			</optgroup>
			<option value="10">Aufgaben</option>
			<option value="11">Meine Dateien</option>
			<option value="12">Neuigkeiten</option>
			<option value="13">Termine</option>
			<option value="14">Lern-Store</option>
			<optgroup label="Verwaltung">
				<option value="15">Registrierung & Login</option>
				<option value="16">Berechtigungen</option>
				<option value="17">IDM (LDAP, SSO, TSP etc.)</option>
			</optgroup>
			<optgroup label="Weiteres">
				<option value="18">Apps</option>
				<option value="19">Benachrichtigungen</option>
				<option value="20">Messenger</option>
			</optgroup>
			<option value="21">Zuordnung nicht möglich</option>
		</select>
</label>
</center>

<label class="control-label">Ist das Problem bereits bekannt?</label>
<p id="inline_text">Hast du geschaut, ob dein Problem bereits bekannt ist? Denn es hilft uns schneller voran zu kommen, wenn nur neue Probleme mitgeteilt werden.
</p>

<iframe class="full" src="https://docs.hpi-schul-cloud.org/display/SCDOK/Bekannte+Fehler+in+der+Cloud+und+ihre+Behebung"
    frameborder="0" scrolling="yes">
</iframe>

<label class="control-label">Hier kannst du schauen, ob aktuelle Probleme bei den technischen Systemen vorliegen: <a href="https://status.hpi-schul-cloud.de/">Status-Seite</a></label>

<h4 class="icon-card__title">Support kontaktieren</h4>
<span class="icon-card__subtitle">Dein Problem ist nicht dabei? Kontaktiere den Support.</span>

<label class="form-group">
	<span class="control-label">{{$t "help.global.label.briefDescriptionOfTheProblem" }}</span>
	<input class="form-control" type="text" name="title" placeholder="{{$t "help.placeholder.briefDescriptionOfTheProblem" }}" required>
</label>
<label class="form-group">
	<span class="control-label">{{$t "help.form_bug.label.problemDescription" }}</span>
<textarea class="form-control" cols="50" name="problemDescription" rows="14" required></textarea>
</label>
<label class="form-group">
	<span class="control-label optional">{{$t "help.form_bug.label.theProblemOccursOnTheDevice" }}</span>
	<input type="text" name="device" placeholder="z.B. iPhone X, Samsung Galaxy S10" class="form-control">
</label>
<label class="form-group">
	<span class="control-label">
		{{$t "help.global.label.replyEmail" }}
	</span>
	<input class="form-control" type="email" name="replyEmail" placeholder="{{$t "help.placeholder.email"}}" value="{{ userEmail }}" required>
</label>
<hr>
<fieldset>
	<legend class="control-legend">{{$t "help.global.label.furtherInformation" }}</legend>
    <label for="consent">
        <div class="row">
	        <div id="consent_checkbox">
		        <input type="checkbox" id="consent" name="consent" value="true" checked>
	        </div>
	        <div>
		        <span class="control-label">
			    {{{$t "help.form_bug.text.iAgreeThatTheFollowingInformationMayBe" }}}
		        </span>
	        </div>
        </div>
    </label>
</fieldset>
{{#ifEnv "FEATURE_CONTACT_FORM_ATTACHMENTS_ENABLED" "true"}}
<br>
<label class="form-group">
    <span class="control-label">{{$t "help.form_bug.label.maxSizeFiles" }} (max. {{ @root.MAXIMUM_ALLOWABLE_TOTAL_ATTACHMENTS_SIZE_MEGABYTE }}MB):</span>
    <input type="file" class="form-control-file" name="file" multiple="multiple" accept="image/*,video/*,application/msword,application/pdf"
		data-max-attachment-size-mb="{{ @root.MAXIMUM_ALLOWABLE_TOTAL_ATTACHMENTS_SIZE_MEGABYTE }}">
</label>
{{/ifEnv}}
<hr>
<span class="control-label file-alert"></span>
